thread.title: William Buchanan
thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da William Buchanan

author: William Buchanan
title: William Buchanan
text:
I decided to get new ray bans and looked everywhere. I found otticanet.com and their prices were unbeatable and the product was genuine and new.
After purchasing the new sunglasses I realised they are not in my home country of Australia and I started to worry but after a quick look over their website and the emails received after purchase I was quickly reassured it was safe and legitimate.
Extremely satisfied with otticanet
